Name: devansh
Mythic_Story: devansh, born under traits Cancer, Dhanu, Purva Ashadha, Manushya, is guided by Saraswati and guarded by Phoenix. Shadow trials arise from Rahu, Eris, and Loki, forging a mythic journey of self-mastery.
